@wp.kernel

    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0

    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.91)) + wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.11)))
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.80 / v2 + 0.30)) - 0.47)
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.72)))
    data[tid] = v0
